g.text: + to OB_MENU: right click on canvas
+ to CANVAS_MOVE: mouse down and move
+ to OBSERVE: click item: reposition tree
+ to TE_MENU: right click on tree
+ to TE_CANVAS_MOVE: mouse down and move on root
+ to TE_ATTACH_MOVE: mouse down and move on non-root
+ to TE_INPUT_TEXT: !pluginBinded && double click on tree
+ to TREE_EDIT: create tree: click item: create child
+ to TREE_EDIT: create tree: click item: create sibling
+ to TREE_EDIT: edit tree: click item: delete
+ to TREE_EDIT: edit tree: click item: cut
+ to TREE_EDIT: edit tree: click item: copy
+ to TREE_EDIT: edit tree: click item: paste
+ to TREE_EDIT: mouse up on canvas
+ mouseup on tree: append as child
+ mouseup on tree: append as sibling
